      "text": [
        " «إِذَا نُظِّفَ وَ أُصْلِحَ فَلاَ بَأْسَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.711 - Abu Al-Hasan al-Awwal, Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about a house that had been used as a latrine for a period of time and whether it would be suitable to make it into a mosque.\nImam (as) said: \"If it is cleaned and repaired, then there is no harm.\""
        ]
      }
